{
  "name": "RPlog_16_ABY_Imperial_Gala_Ball",
  "title": "16 ABY: Imperial Gala Ball",
  "summary": "The Imperial Gala moves into the grand ballroom of the Coruscant museum, where officers and dignitaries pair off for dancing and conversation beneath the chandeliers. Flight Officer Liza Molokai trades dry banter with the perpetually uncomfortable ISB Agent Dreven, while the squadronmate Odion and the late-arriving Solon Halwinder drift along the margins. Marshal Krieg coaxes the reluctant Jeni -- under her Shael persona -- onto the floor, and the courtly Xy'lear strikes up a charming rapport with the Corporate Sector visitor Inaya near the buffet. Meanwhile the Sith Warlord Davyd arrives on the arm of the former Admiral Petra, Squadron Leader Dante mingles with the urbane Malif, and Warlord Korolov takes his seat at the head table as red-armored Royal Guardsmen file in. The evening unfolds as a tapestry of dances, polite deflections, veiled flirtations, and gracious farewells as the guests gradually pair away across the vast ballroom.",
